title: Bengali Beef Strip Curry with Rice NEW | Pre-Prepped | Three Steps | Ready in 15
description: With pre-chopped, pre-marinated ingredients, our new Fresh & Fast recipes are on the table in just 15 minutes. Perfect for busy weeknights - and busy people. This week, we've got a mild, yet flavourful Bengal beef curry with coriander and crushed peanuts.

*Heads-up - you'll need a microwave for this recipe.*
